    "content": "<div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B0000 0%, #DC143C 50%, #8B0000 100%); padding: 100px 20px; text-align: center; color: white;\"><h1 style=\"font-size: 4em; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #FFD700;\">Jai Guruji</h1><p style=\"font-size: 1.5em; font-style: italic;\">The Path of Love and Surrender</p><a href=\"/about\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-top: 30px; padding: 15px 40px; background: #FFD700; color: #8B0000; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;\">Learn More</a></div><div style=\"padding: 60px 20px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;\"><h2 style=\"text-align: center; color: #8B0000;\">About Guruji</h2><div style=\"width: 100px; height: 4px; background: #DC143C; margin: 20px auto;\"></div><p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.8;\">Nirmal Singh Maharaj (1952-2007), lovingly called Guruji, was a divine spiritual master who touched millions of lives through his blessings. His teachings emphasized the unity of all religions, love, compassion, and selfless service.</p><div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; margin-top: 50px;\"><div style=\"text-align: center; padding: 30px; background: #FFF5F5; border-radius: 10px;\"><h3 style=\"color: #8B0000;\">Bada Mandir</h3><p>Visit the sacred Shiv Mandir in Chhatarpur, Delhi - Guruji's samadhi shrine and a place of miraculous healings.</p></div><div style=\"text-align: center; padding: 30px; background: #FFF5F5; border-radius: 10px;\"><h3 style=\"color: #8B0000;\">Daily Sangats</h3><p>Join spiritual congregations featuring meditation, satsang, Gurbani recitations, and blessed langar.</p></div><div style=\"text-align: center; padding: 30px; background: #FFF5F5; border-radius: 10px;\"><h3 style=\"color: #8B0000;\">Divine Blessings</h3><p>Experience Guruji's grace through his immortal words: \"Kalyan karta\" and \"Blessings always.\"</p></div></div></div><div style=\"background: #8B0000; padding: 60px 20px; color: white;\"><div style=\"max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;\"><h2 style=\"color: #FFD700;\">Sacred Shabads</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">Connect with the divine through these blessed hymns</p><div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NmYRoxPkfRs\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block; padding: 20px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 8px; color: white; text-decoration: none;\">Mool Mantra</a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kR2hC0Lp4aI\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block; padding: 20px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 8px; color: white; text-decoration: none;\">Japji Sahib</a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HS8xQ9mKTgE\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block; padding: 20px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 8px; color: white; text-decoration: none;\">Gurbani Kirtan</a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block; padding: 20px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 8px; color: white; text-decoration: none;\">Shabad Hazare</a></div></div></div><div style=\"padding: 60px 20px; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;\"><h2 style=\"color: #8B0000;\">Devotee Experiences</h2><p style=\"font-style: italic; font-size: 1.2em; margin: 30px 0;\">\"Guruji changed my life. His blessings cured my illness when nothing else worked. I felt his presence strongest at Bada Mandir.\"</p><p style=\"color: #DC143C; font-weight: bold;\">- A Devoted Follower</p></div><div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #DC143C, #8B0000); padding: 60px 20px; color: white; text-align: center;\"><h2 style=\"color: #FFD700;\">Join Our Sangat</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">Whether you're seeking healing, peace, or spiritual growth, Guruji's doors are always open.</p><a href=\"/home-satsang\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 15px 40px; background: #FFD700; color: #8B0000; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 10px;\">Home Satsang</a><a href=\"/contact\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 15px 40px; background: transparent; color: #FFD700; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; border: 2px solid #FFD700;\">Contact Us</a></div>"
}